"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-04-25-andy-murrays-psychologist-targets-olympic-gold-medal-paris-games-20716197\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Andy Murray's psychologist Rich Hampson has teamed up with BMX freestyler Kieran Reilly and is targeting Olympic gold at theParisGames.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 135, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 11, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.8074135114484958e-42, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 27, \"end\": 31, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rich_Hardbeck\", \"score\": 0.991091459442182, \"rank\": 0.008987440901207991, \"text\": \"Rich\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rich_Hardbeck\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rich_Hardbeck\"}, {\"begin\": 59, \"end\": 62, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"score\": 0.9977931540078865, \"rank\": 0.0021936749595528634, \"text\": \"BMX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\"}, {\"begin\": 74, \"end\": 80, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kieran_Mitchell\", \"score\": 0.8793379038641398, \"rank\": 0.13712029061759717, \"text\": \"Kieran\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kieran_Mitchell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kieran_Mitchell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hampson featured in theAmazonPrime documentary 'Resurfacing' - a film that followed Murray's incredible injury comeback after he returned with a metal hip.\", \"from\": 137, \"to\": 292, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 221, \"end\": 227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0755627808586816e-25, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray's psychologist has now swapped tennis for BMX as he looks to help Reilly secure a gold medal for Britain at theOlympic Gamesin Paris this summer.\", \"from\": 294, \"to\": 446, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 294, \"end\": 300, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0755627808586816e-25, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 343, \"end\": 346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"score\": 0.9977931540078865, \"rank\": 0.0021936749595528634, \"text\": \"BMX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\"}, {\"begin\": 398, \"end\": 405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9950586968002748, \"rank\": 0.004963913355861911, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's very new to me,' Reilly said about working with Hampson.\", \"from\": 448, \"to\": 510, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I was sceptical at first because it's so new to our sport.\", \"from\": 511, \"to\": 570, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I have not heard of anyone else using it, so I did not see the benefit.\", \"from\": 572, \"to\": 644, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But it's not so much psychology, it's more just breaking things down.\", \"from\": 645, \"to\": 714, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Like when you say a certain trick is scary, you are then building that image to yourself.\", \"from\": 716, \"to\": 806, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'When you start working with him, you realise, 'Oh yeah, you are really in your own head' - little things can have a massive impact, like doing a certain routine before you drop in so that it feels the same every time.'\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 1027, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray recentlyreturned to practiceafter his horror ankle injury at the Miami Open, although no timeline for his ATP Tour comeback has been announced.\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1179, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1029, \"end\": 1035, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0755627808586816e-25, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 36-year-old, who has admitted he'sunlikely to play past this summeras he edges towards retirement, ishoping to featureat the upcoming Olympics.\", \"from\": 1181, \"to\": 1328, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray won Olympic gold in the men's singles at London 2012 and Rio 2016 while he has also landed a silver medal in mixed doubles with Laura Robson.\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1478, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1330, \"end\": 1336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0755627808586816e-25, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 1465, \"end\": 1477, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Robson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laura Robson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Robson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Robson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The three-time Grand Slam champion is 'out of the walking boot' and has been seen hitting forehand shots on an indoor practice court.\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1613, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was previously thought that Murray could have been ruled outfor up to 12 monthsbut his team have since confirmed that he has avoided surgery.\", \"from\": 1615, \"to\": 1759, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1646, \"end\": 1652, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0755627808586816e-25, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am looking forward to the end [of my career] now,' Murray said last month.\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 1838, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1815, \"end\": 1821, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0755627808586816e-25, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'[I will] give my best the next few months.'\", \"from\": 1839, \"to\": 1883, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:I am desperate to tell the real stories behind our extraordinary Olympians  ArrowMORE:BBC will not use Team GB legend for coverage of Paris Olympics  ArrowMORE:French diver fails to make a splash after embarrassing slip in front of Emmanuel Macron  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 2254, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1981, \"end\": 1984, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9262595899699114, \"rank\": 0.07926353747761988, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q